The Etsu Kwali in the FCT, Alhaji Shaban Audu Nizazo III, has stressed on need for his people, especially in the rural areas, to always monitor government projects sited in their localities. Alhaji Shaban, represented by Chief Victor Basil, spoke at a stakeholders meeting in Gwagwalada Area Council on Tuesday. He said the stakeholders meeting on monitoring of projects was an eye opener to every individual, especially people in rural communities, to be conscious of government projects sited in their communities.